November 09, 2012 8:39am

Boldly styled, bob hairstyle given a tousled reworking, Karlie Kloss covers the June 2013 issue of Vogue Turkey.

On the cover (previewed after the break) Kloss wears a deeply plunging leopard print swimsuit, while a preview of the editorial shows more animal prints, swimwear and statement accessories.
